Lastly, we show that CLMR generalises to out-of-domain datasets by pre-training it on entirely different music datasets. Pre-training is performed on the Million Song Dataset, FMA, Billboard and GTZAN separately and linear evaluation is performed on the MagnaTagATune dataset. https://t.co/pIVsiKxSOt

When fine-tuning the linear classifier (only!) using the self-supervised learned representations on 1% of the labels (= 259 songs for MagnaTagATune), it still achieves 33.1% AP. A linear classifier trained on our self-supervised representations matches fully supervised SampleCNN on the MagnaTagATune dataset (our average precision is 35.4% vs. 34.4% for supervised training).
